```

// 0x3882114BDE571AD4
// 0xC1213A21
ENTITY::SET_ENTITY_INVINCIBLE(Entity entity, BOOL toggle);
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
```

Sets a ped or an object totally invincible. It doesn't take any kind of damage. Peds will not ragdol
l on explosions and the tazer animation won't apply either.  

If you use this for a ped and you want Ragdoll to stay enabled, then do:  

*(DWORD *)(pedAddress + 0x188) |= (1 << 9);  

Use this if you want to get the invincibility status:  

	bool IsPedInvincible(Ped ped)  

	{  

auto addr = getScriptHandleBaseAddress(ped);	  

if (addr)  

{  

	DWORD flag = *(DWORD *)(addr + 0x188);  

	return ((flag & (1 << 8)) != 0) || ((flag & (1 << 9)) != 0);  

}  

return false;  

	}  

