```

// 0x5CE62918F8D703C7 // 0xDF552973 GRAPHICS::_0x5CE62918F8D703C7(int lowR, int lowG, int lowB, int lowAlpha, int R, int G, int B, int Alpha, ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- highR, int highG, int highB, int highAlpha);
```
This native is used along with these two natives: [`0xa356990e161c9e65`](https://runtime.fivem.net/d oc/reference.html#_0xA356990E161C9E65) and [`0x1c4fc5752bcd8e48`](https://runtime.fivem.net/doc/refe rence.html#_0x1C4FC5752BCD8E48).
This native sets the colors for the golf putting grid. the 'min...' values are for the lower areas t hat the grid covers, the 'max...' values are for the higher areas that the grid covers, all remainin g values are for the 'normal' ground height.
All those natives combined they will output something like this: https://i.imgur.com/TC6cku6.png
