// 0x9414E18B9434C2FE // 0x60746B88 PED::SET_PED_HEAD_BLEND_DATA(Ped ped, int shapeFirstID, int shapeSecondID, int shapeThirdID, int ski ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- stID, int skinSecondID, int skinThirdID, float shapeMix, float skinMix, float thirdMix, BOOL isP arent);
```
```
The "shape" parameters control the shape of the ped's face. The "skin" parameters control the skin t one. ShapeMix and skinMix control how much the first and second IDs contribute,(typically mother and father.) ThirdMix overrides the others in favor of the third IDs. IsParent is set for "children" of the player character's grandparents during old-gen character creation. It has unknown effect otherw ise.
The IDs start at zero and go Male Non-DLC, Female Non-DLC, Male DLC, and Female DLC.
